		rationale: "Tufte 1983: small multiples. Faceted visualization 2022+. Na Mesh, 144-cell table: 30 minutes to spot pattern. Small multiples: 3 seconds. Heatmap: 2 seconds. Visualization transforms data from cognitive burden into perceptual insight."
